			Results of yesterday
		</h1>

		<div class="center " style="flex-direction: column;width:90%;" >

			<button class=" btn123 darkcolor bordercolor">
				<div class="my-div">
					<div class="my-div">
							<p style="font-size:25px">
								<span> NGA </span>
								<span class="span2"> 16 </span>
								<span class="span2"> vs </span>
								<span class="span2"> 11 </span>
								<span> WAS </span>
								<span style ="text-align: right;">Blast.tv Paris Major 2022</span>
							</p>
						

					</div>

				</div>
			</button>

			<h1 style="text-align: right;margin-right:30%">
			Results of today
			</h1>

			<button class=" btn123 darkcolor bordercolor" style="margin-left:30%">
				<div class="my-div" >
						<span style="text-align: center;">
							<p style="font-size:25px">
								<span> Fnatic </span>
								<span class="span2"> 16 </span>
								<span class="span2"> vs </span>
								<span class="span2"> 10 </span>
								<span> SAW </span>
								<span >Blast.tv Paris Major 2022</span>
							</p>
						</span>

				</div>
			</button>

		</div>

	</div>
</body>
</html>

